data.description: Discover modern comfort in this 2020-built gem nestled in the coveted Citrus Isle community of Davenport. Spanning 2,966 sqft, this five-bedroom, three-bathroom haven boasts a main-floor master, creating a perfect retreat. Revel in the seamless blend of style and functionality with tile flooring throughout the downstairs living spaces and plush carpets in the bedrooms and upstairs.    The property is fully fenced with a stylish vinyl fence for added privacy. Step into luxury with numerous upgrades, including a cutting-edge SMART home system. The kitchen is a culinary delight with oversized cabinetry, granite countertops, and high-end appliances. The spacious laundry room is equipped with ample counter space and cabinets for ultimate convenience.    Immerse yourself in the contemporary elegance of this turnkey residence, where every detail has been thoughtfully curated for modern living. Welcome home to a perfect blend of sophistication and comfort in the heart of Citrus Isle.
